Umubare w'abanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) uzamuka cyane mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Iyo umuntu wese wanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) agaragaye mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ibyo byemeza ko nubwo ibipimo bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, COVID-19 ishobora gukwirakwira mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije uko ibintu bimeze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bigomba kwitegura kwakira abarwayi benshi cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu benshi basanganywe indwara y'ubuhumekero itaramenyekana mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo cyatewe n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus ubu buzwi nka SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye kwitwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubuhamya buhari bugaragaza ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite ibibazo byoroheje, urugero nk'indwara yo guhumeka cyangwa guhumeka nabi, kandi ko abenshi muri bo bashobora gukira.
Mu bantu 14%, COVID-19 iterwa n'uburwayi bukomeye bukenera kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho 6% iraterwa n'uburwayi bukomeye bukenera kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abinjiwe mu bitaro bazira COVID-19 bashobora gupfa ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugiye kureba uko ibintu byose bya COVID-19 byagenze muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EEA) no mu Bwongereza, tugereranyije n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Tuzagereranya kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 yageze mu bindi bihugu kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 kizakwirakwira mu bindi bihugu nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, mu kiganiro cyitwa Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri na bagenzi be bavuze ku bantu ba mbere bo mu Burayi banduye COVID-19 nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, abantu batatu ba mbere banduye mu Bufaransa ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020, ni abantu bari bavuye i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa bagarutse mu Bufaransa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu bari baranduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza, kandi kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu, abantu 39,768 bamaze kwandura COVID-19 n'abantu 1,727 bamaze gupfa, mu Butaliyani honyine honyine hamaze kwandura abantu 17,750 naho mu Butaliyani honyine hamaze gupfa abantu 1,441.
Gushyiraho imibare yose n'imibare y'abanduye COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), cyatangaje imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byose, ikurikije amakuru yemewe n'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima ku isi n'iz'akarere, na OMS, buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ndetse no mu Butaliyani.
Ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, dufata iminsi 14 nk'iminsi y'ubukangurambaga bwa COVID-19, bityo tukagenzura uko COVID-19 yagenze mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twagereranyije imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Igeragezwa ry'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, rizakurikiza ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Umurongo wa 1).
Ku bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma buza ku kigero cyo hejuru ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu mu Butaliyani, ariko mu bihugu byose byo mu Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wariyongereye cyane (Izindi nkuru).
Umubare 2 ugaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi birerekana ko, ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abanduye nk'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 izamuka cyane mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo kizakwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi.
Ibi ni ko bimeze nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibipimo bitandukanye, abashinzwe ubuvuzi batandukanye, kandi hari igihe usanga hari ibisobanuro bitandukanye ku bihugu bitandukanye, ndetse n'amategeko atandukanye agenga icyemezo cy'abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, ndetse n'ibipimo by'inyongera.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu Butaliyani bavugaga ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibyumba by'ibitaro by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri ako karere byuzuye.
Amakuru y'abanduye COVID-19 bari mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye ubu ari mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, aho ari 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntagaragara).
Icyakora, bagomba kubishyira hamwe kugira ngo byongere ku makuru mashya arebana n'umubare w'abandura n'uw'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi bwo hagati, abantu benshi cyane bari mu bitaro byabakira cyane n'ibitanda byo mu bitaro, aho mu Budage bari 29,2 ku bantu 100.000, naho muri Porutugali bari 4,2.
Bisobanura ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ubushobozi bwinshi cyangwa buke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12,5 mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ibitanda by'indembe ku bantu 100.000 mu 201011).
Gutegura uburyo bwo kwita ku barwayi byararenze ubushobozi bw'abaganga, kuko imibare igera kuri yose y'ibihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza yerekana abantu bavurwa COVID-19 n'umubare w'abantu bari mu kaga ko kubura ibitanda mu bitaro byita ku barwayi cyane ugera kuri 90% byatanzwe n'ibyavuye mu cyemezo cya gatandatu gishya cy'ikigo ECDC cy'isuzuma ry'ibihe bidasanzwe bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko abarwayi benshi baba mu bihugu byo mu Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'i Burayi n'u Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro byo mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bikunze gukoreshwa mu gucumbikira abantu bo mu karere runaka, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda byita ku barwayi bakomeye agomba kuboneka mu gice cyitwa Nomenclature y'ibice by'amakuru by'urwego rwa 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibiri kuba mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora gukwirakwira mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kwitegura uko bizakora mu gihe hazaba hari abantu benshi banduye SARS-CoV-2 n'umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 bashaka kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa n'ikigo ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bw'ingirakamaro kandi bw'ingirakamaro ni ngombwa mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, mu gukuraho abantu banduye no kugabanya ibiciro byo kubungabunga ubwandu; kuko kumenya umubare w'abanduye mu buryo bw'ibanze bitanga umusaruro ku bantu bafata ibyemezo kandi ibitaro ntibishobora kubona umwanya wo kubisobanukirwa, kubyemera no kwitegura kubikora mu gihe nta kizamini cya mbere cyakozwe.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibyago byihutirwa kandi bwerekeza ku ngamba nyinshi z'ubuvuzi rusange zigamije kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito ibihugu bifite umwanya wo kongera ingufu mu gushyiraho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no gushyiraho igitutu ku buvuzi.
Iyo bitabaye ibyo, inzego z'ubuzima mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe byo mu Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi zishobora kongera umubare w'abarwayi, bigasaba ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere bajya mu bitaro bya ICU.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000, ndetse cyongera ubwandu ku bantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma kiba icyorezo gikomeye ku isi.
Mu buryo buhuje n'ubwoko bwa virusi ya SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barwara SARS mu mwaka wa 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yarakomotse ku mbogo, kandi ikaba ifite ibimenyetso n'uburyo bwo kwanduza.
Nubwo COVID-19 idafite ubukana bwinshi kandi idashobora kwica cyane nka SARS, ariko irandura cyane kandi igera ku bantu bakuru kurusha abakiri bato, kandi igera ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko ibitabo by'iyi ndwara bizakomeza kwandikwa, iyi ngingo igamije gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi agaragaza ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bizakorwa kuri iyi ngingo.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ingenzi birebana n'indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, impamvu zitera iyo ndwara, uko zikwirakwira, uko zifatwa, uko zivurwa, uko umuntu ashobora kuzirwanya n'uko yakwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi ngingo izagufasha kumenya no kurwanya iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana mu mateka y'Abashinwa, kuko bari barahawe amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'uwo munsi mukuru ndetse no mu gihe cy'ibyumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo gishya cy'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yiswe SARS mu mwaka wa 2003; ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara yavuye kuri iyo virusi yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iyo ndwara y'icyorezo yatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze ihita ikwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi y'icyorezo yari imaze kwandura abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 barakira, abandi barenga 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS iratangaza ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'abantu wa mbere" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Dukurikije PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, abagore banditse ingingo zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 harimo n'iby'ubwandu, indwara z'ibyorezo, imiterere y'umubiri, uburyo bwo kuyigenzura n'uburyo bwo kuyivura, kuva batanga raporo ya mbere ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 igaragaza uko virusi ikwirakwira mu bantu benshi.
Iyi ngingo izagerageza gusobanura muri make iby'ubushakashatsi buzakorwa kuri icyo cyorezo gishya.
Aho bishoboka, tugerageza guhuza COVID-19 na SARS hamwe n'indi ndwara ya CoV, indwara yo guhumeka yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, yavutse mu mwaka wa 2012).
Nanone kandi, turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uko indwara y'ibicurane ishobora guhangana n'uko izaba imeze, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
Hari abavuga ko CoVs atari indwara z'uburwayi zikomeye cyane, cyane cyane ko zigera ku kigero cya 15% by'abanduye indwara z'ibicurane 4.
Ariko kandi, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'izindi virusi za CoV zishobora kwanduza abantu incuro ebyiri, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiranye n'icyorezo cy'i Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, maze zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu vuba na bwangu, zigira ingaruka zikomeye ku barwayi ndetse n'abahitanwa na zo.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni CoV ya gatatu yongeye kugaragara mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'imibare. Icyorezo cya 1,1, cy'uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero butaramenyekana aho buturuka, cyatangajwe bwa mbere i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Gashyantare 2019 n'ikigo cy'ubushinjacyaha mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, basanze icyorezo cya CoV gitangiye.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye i Wuhan.
Icyo gihe, iyo ndwara yakwirakwiraga mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku itariki ya 20, hatangajwe ko basanze iyo ndwara, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko ishobora kwandurira umuntu ku wundi.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunzwe, kandi imodoka za Leta ntizikora.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, hatangiye iperereza ku cyorezo, mu bantu 41 banduye, 21 gusa ni bo bageze ku isoko ry'amafi y'inyanja rya Wuhan aho icyorezo cyatangiriye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iyi ndwara ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Mu gihe twandikaga iyi raporo, iki cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Ibisubizo. (Ibisubizo.2).2).
Uko ibintu bizagenda byihuta, uko bizagenda bigera ku rugero rungana kose n'ukuntu bizagenda bigenda birushaho gukomera, ntibizwi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 8.866 harimo n'abantu 4.021 bafite COVID-19 bwerekanye amakuru mashya y'icyorezo nk'uko biri hasi aha (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane abantu bafite imyaka 30-65.
