Remdesivir ni umuti urwanya virusi watangiriye gukoreshwa mu ishuri rya Gileyadi mu kuvura Ebola na Marlburg.
Nyuma yaho, umuti wa remdesivir wagaragaye ko ushobora gukoreshwa mu kurwanya izindi virusi ziterwa na RNA, harimo na MERS na SARS.
Mu rwego rwo kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abaturage, Gilead yatanze ibi bikoresho mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bigerweho n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi abantu bategereje cyane ibisubizo byabyo.
Nanone kandi, baricitinbe, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin, byavuzwe ko bishobora gufasha abantu bafite ibibazo bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Kugira iseseme, kuruka, kuruka, kurwara impyiko n'ibindi bibazo bishobora guterwa no guhuza iyi miti na lopinavir/ritonavir.
Iyo imiti ikoreshejwe mu kuvura abarwayi, igomba kugenzurwa cyane.
Abakize bakira amaraso n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi
Guteranyiriza hamwe amaraso y'abantu barokotse icyorezo kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwaye icyo cyorezo cyangwa kugira ngo barinde abantu bafite amagara mazima indwara z'ibyorezo, byatangiye kera cyane.
Mu by'ukuri, abakize akenshi baba bafite abasirikare bakomeye mu maraso yabo barwanya mikorobe.
Imiti igwanya indwara ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo za B mu kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bintu byangiza, kandi ikamenya molekile zanduye zikazirimbura.
Muri iki gihe, akenshi bafata plasma mu maraso y'abarwayi barwaye COVID-19 kandi bakayisangiza abantu 10 barwaye cyane.
Nyuma y'amasaha 24, barushijeho kumva bamerewe neza, kandi indwara ya virusi yari imaze kubagabanuka, bituma amaraso yabo atagira umwuka wa ogisijeni.
Ariko kandi, kugira ngo twemeze ko uburyo bwo kuvura bukoreshwa mbere y'uko umuti uvura indwara uvugwa mu buryo bw'ukuri, tugomba kubanza kugenzura no gusobanura neza uko bimeze.
Nanone kandi, kubera ko umuti ushobora guteza akaga, hari ibindi bintu bishobora guteza akaga bishobora guterwa na plasma.
Urugero, uduhimba tw'umubiri dushobora gutuma umubiri udakora neza, kandi tukagira uruhare mu gutuma habaho utwo turemangingo twitwa cytokines, twangiza ubuzima.
Ubusanzwe, amaraso n'umubiri bigira imikorere y'umubiri itandukanye, kandi kuvurwa hakoreshejwe plasma ni byo bikenewe cyane.
Gukora no gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi tw'ubwoko runaka kugira ngo turwanye indwara z'ibyorezo, biragoye.
Ni yo mpamvu ari ngombwa kandi bihuje n'ubwenge gutandukanya utwo turemangingo twa B tw'abantu barokotse maze tukamenya ubushobozi bw'izo ndwara cyangwa tukabitwara kugira ngo tumenye niba izo ndwara zishobora kurwanya poroteyine za virusi.
Ibyo bituma dushobora gukora za antibodies vuba.
Mu Bushinwa, ubuvuzi bw'imiti bw'agakabyo bwamaze imyaka myinshi bukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka ziterwa no kuba hari ibintu byinshi bivangwa mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'uburwayi, bitewe n'uko umuti w'amaraso ukoreshwa.
Hari ibintu byinshi by'ingirakamaro bitaramenyekana cyangwa bitamenyekana neza kubera ko bigoye kubyerekana no kubigenzura no kubishyira hamwe.
Kubera ko ubu nta muti wa COVID-19 ufite imbaraga kandi wizewe, TCM yabaye umuti w'ingenzi ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa abavuwe indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, abantu basanze imiti ya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen ari ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Umubare munini w'abantu bakize COVID-19 wabonetse mu ntara nyinshi z'Ubushinwa zikoresha TCM ku barwayi bagera kuri 87%, harimo Gansu (63,7%), Ningxia (50%), na Hunan (50%), ariko mu ntara ya Hubei, ikoresha TCM ku barwayi bagera kuri 30% gusa ba COVID-19, habonetse umuntu umwe (13%).
Ariko kandi, ibyo kugereranya biragoye kubera ko hari ibindi bintu, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bw'indwara, bigomba kwitabwaho mu gihe cyo gusuzuma.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya imiti y'u Burayi (WM) n'imiti ya WM na TCM.
Babonye ko igihe cyo kugabanya ubushyuhe, kugabanya ibimenyetso no kuba mu bitaro cyari gito mu itsinda rya WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda rya WM gusa.
Igitangaje cyane ni uko ubwiyongere bw'ibimenyetso (kuva ku buto kugeza ku bukomeye) bwari buke cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda rya WM gusa (7,4% kuri 46,2%) kandi urupfu rwari ruto mu itsinda rya WM+TCM kurusha mu itsinda rya WM gusa (8,8% kuri 39%).
Icyakora, nta kindi kigaragaza ko TCM ifite akamaro n'uko ikora neza, uretse kugerageza kuyikoresha mu bantu benshi no mu turere twinshi.
Nanone kandi, bizatuma abantu barushaho kumenya imiterere y'imiti n'ukuntu ishobora gukoreshwa mu buvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa se uko ikoreshwa mu buryo buhuje n'imiti.
Abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19 bakunze kugira ubwoba bw'indwara ishobora kubateza urupfu, kandi abantu bari mu kato barushaho guhangayika, bakumva bari mu bwigunge no kurakara.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara, urugero nk'umuriro mwinshi, kubura umwuka mwiza n'ubuhumekero, hamwe n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'imiti, urugero nk'indwara yo kubura ibitotsi iterwa na korticosteroide, bishobora gutuma umuntu ahangayika cyane kandi agahangayika.
Mu gihe SARS yatangiraga, abantu bagaragaye ko bafite imyifatire myinshi, urugero nko kwiheba cyane, guhangayika, kugira ubwoba, kugira imyifatire idakwiriye, kwibagirwa, gutakaza ubwenge ndetse no gushaka kwiyahura.
Gushakisha abantu bagiranye isano n'ubwandu no gushyira abantu mu kato kugira ngo barinde COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu bagira imihangayiko n'umubabaro bitewe no kwanduza abandi, kuba mu kato, no kubabaza imiryango n'incuti.
Ni yo mpamvu bagomba guha ubwisungane mu kwivuza abantu bafite COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho kuyandura, n'abandi bose babikeneye.
Ubuvuzi bw'abantu bugomba kuba bushingiye ku gushyiraho itsinda ry'abantu benshi bafasha abantu, gushyikirana mu buryo bworoshye no gutanga amakuru agezweho kandi y'ukuri ku byerekeye icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imiti, hamwe no gukora no gukoresha ibikoresho na porogaramu byo kwirinda kwihererana.
Inkingo z'ukuri ni ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu mu nyamaswa no mu bantu ndetse no mu bindi binyabuzima, kandi akenshi zihuza n'imiti ya virusi mu kurwanya indwara zikomeye ziterwa n'ubwandu bushya.
Hateganyijwe ko hazakorwa ubushakashatsi mu bijyanye no gukora urukingo rw'umushongi wa S, kugira ngo ruzatange udukoko tw'umubiri tw'igihe kirekire kandi dushobora kwica no/cyangwa kurinda abantu SARS-CoV.
Abagore bagerageje inkingo z'ubuzima ku mafi z'ubwoko bwa SARS.
Ariko kandi, nta cyizere cy'uko inkingo zifite ingaruka ku bantu bageze mu za bukuru n'abarwaye indwara zikomeye, ndetse n'uko zitagira ubukana ku mikorobe zaturutse ku nyamaswa, kugeza igihe hatangiriye gukorwa ubushakashatsi ku bantu.
Birashoboka ko ari uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 kandi nta wundi muntu wigeze ayandura kuva icyo gihe.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, abantu ku giti cyabo n'amatsinda y'abantu bazakomeza kwandura MERS mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, kandi izakwirakwira mu tundi duce bitewe n'uko ituruka mu nyamaswa.
Abagore bakoze ubushakashatsi ku buryo bakwirakwiza urukingo rwa MERS mu kwica virusi, ADN y'ingirabuzimafatizo, ibikoresho by'ubwandu, uduhimba duto cyane, ibintu bisa n'ibikoresho bya virusi n'uduce twa poroteyine ya virusi, ndetse n'ibindi byakozwe ku nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rukomeye kandi rukora neza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu batanduye ni ingenzi kandi ni akazi gakomeye mu kugabanya icyorezo.
Ariko kandi, biragoye guhangana n'ibibazo biterwa n'igihe kirekire (kimwe n'amezi 18) cyo gukora inkingo, hamwe n'ubwoko bwinshi bwa CoV.
Kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, itangiye kugaragara mu bantu bake cyane.
Incuro nyinshi, abarwayi bashobora gukira batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Ariko nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS na MERS, COVID-19 izatera ubwoba abarwayi kandi izateza urupfu abarwayi bakomeye.
Ni yo mpamvu, uburyo bwo gupima indwara ari ingenzi ku baganga kugira ngo bashyire imbere umurimo wabo, cyane cyane mu turere dufite ubushobozi buke.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bagore, ibi bikurikira bishobora kugira uruhare cyangwa bigira aho bihuriye n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kumenya uko SARS izagenda, kandi ni na ko bimeze ku birebana na COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibonekeje cyane cyane mu bantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65, kuko 47,7% by'abarwayi bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8.866 bavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'indwara n'ububabare kandi bararama igihe kirekire kurusha abataragaragaje ibimenyetso (hagati y'imyaka 66 na 51), bigaragaza ko imyaka ari kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi byerekana ko umuntu ufite COVID-19 ashobora gukira.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo kurusha abagore (0.31/100.000 kuri 0.27/100.000), nk'uko byasobanuwe haruguru.
Ibindi bimenyetso n'ibibazo: Abantu bafite COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bashobora kugira ibibazo by'ubuhumekero n'umutima.
Indwara z'umutima na zo ni zo zatumaga abantu benshi bapfa bitewe na SARS.
Hari abavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba ifite ubushobozi bwo guhuza ACE2 cholangiocytes, bishobora gutuma umuntu atagira ubushobozi bwo gukora neza bw'umwijima mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni iby'ingenzi kumenya ko imyaka n'indwara umuntu yahuye na zo mu gihe cyashize bifitanye isano ya bugufi kandi ko bishobora guhuza.
Ibimenyetso byo mu mavuriro: Urusobe rw'umushongi wa C (CRP) mu maraso rugaragaza uburemere bw'ububabare cyangwa ububabare mu mitsi kandi ruvugwa ko ari kimwe mu bintu bituma indwara igenda, bigatuma umuntu ashobora kubona imiti, kandi amaherezo bikamuhesha ubuzima.
Hari kandi n'ihererekanya ry'ibipimo by'ubukana bwa CRP n'ibimenyetso by'indwara ya COVID-19.
Nanone kandi, urugero rwo hejuru rwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) bishobora kugira uruhare mu kugaragaza niba umuntu ashobora gukira cyangwa atazakira.
Izo poroteyine z'ubumara zagiye zikwirakwira mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, kandi zikururwa mu gihe hari imyanda yangiritse.
Ibyo bituma umutima cyangwa impyiko bitagomba gukora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi: Gufata radiographie y'igituza no kugabanya ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara bigomba gufatwa nk'ingingo z'ingenzi mu gusuzuma niba umuntu ashobora gukira COVID-19 ndetse n'uko yakomeza kurwara.
Gukoresha Steroide: Nk'uko twabivuze haruguru, Steroids ni imiti yo kurwanya indwara ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara.
Kubera ko bakortikosteroide nyinshi zakoreshejwe mu barwayi ba SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barwayi barwaye indwara yo kutagira amaraso, bakagira ubumuga bw'ubuzima bwose kandi ntibagire ubuzima bwiza.
Ku bw'ibyo, mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, bagomba gukoresha imiti ya siteroyide mu gihe gito kandi iri hasi ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Guhangayika: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe COVID-19 yatangiraga, abantu benshi bari bafite ibibazo by'ihungabana bitewe no kumara iminsi myinshi mu kato, guhangayika no kubona abagize umuryango wabo bapfa n'abandi barwaye.
Ni ngombwa ko abantu bahabwa inama z'abaganga kandi bakajya bahabwa ubufasha burambye kugira ngo bajye bahangana n'imihangayiko kandi basubire mu buzima busanzwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bagore, bwerekana ko COVID-19 ifite ibindi bintu bitandukanye na SARS.
Uretse kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwira mu buryo bwo guhumeka bwo hasi, ishobora no gukwirakwira mu buryo bwo guhumeka bwo hejuru, igatanga ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso na busa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere, kimwe n'izindi virusi za CoV zitera ibicurane.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu bafite virusi mu gihe cyayo cya mbere cyangwa mbere y'uko ibaho bashobora kuyikoresha mu buryo bwa buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya iyi ndwara bitoroha.
Ariko kandi, SARS-CoV ishobora kwandura mu gihe umuntu arwaye cyane, ariko ntiyabonetse mu gihe cy'ubwandu.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye kandi kiragoye guhangana na cyo kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Mu Bushinwa, hashyizweho ingamba zikomeye zirimo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu mijyi ihakikije no gukomeza gushyira mu kato abaturage bose mu byiringiro byo guhagarika SARS-CoV-2 ngo idakwirakwira.
Nubwo ibyo byose byateje ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage, umubare w'abarwayi bashya ushobora kugabanuka, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyagendaga kirushaho kugabanuka.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bugaragaza ko iyo mibare izarangira muri Werurwe, kandi ko igihe cyo kuyirinda kizamara amezi 3-4.
Icyakora, hari intiti zimwe na zimwe zitemera ko ibyo ari ukuri.
Paul Hunter, na bagenzi be, batekereza ko COVID-19, ifite ubwandu buruta bwa SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini na bagenzi be bakoze icyitegererezo cy'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 bavuga ko gishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ryo muri Kanada ryavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 yabonye ibice by'ibinyamushongo n'imyanda yo mu muhogo by'abarwayi bakize barangije kuva mu bitaro mu byumweru bibiri bishize, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko iyi virusi nshya ishobora kuba indwara y'ibicurane.
Icyakora, mu Bushinwa hari ibimenyetso bifatika bigaragaza ko uburyo bwo kuvura indwara bufite icyo bugeraho.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byari byarahanuwe ko Ebola yari guhitana abantu bagera hafi kuri miriyoni, naho mu gihe kiri imbere ikazahitana abagera hafi kuri miriyoni n'igice.
Icyakora, amaherezo iyo ndwara yaratsinzwe binyuriye mu gushyiraho amategeko akomeye yo kuyirinda no kuyitarura.
Birashoboka kandi ko, nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugabanuka, amaherezo ikazazimira cyangwa ikazavamo virusi idakomeye ku bantu.
Igereranya hagati y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 n'ubw'icyorezo cya SARS na MERS riri hasi (Mn.55).
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura cyane mu gihe umuntu anuka cyangwa akanywa, kandi ishobora no kwandura mu gihe umuntu yanduye.
Nanone basanze virusi mu byondo, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ishobora kuba yaraturutse mu byondo ikajya mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41 ku ijana by'abarwayi batandukaniye ku barwayi bari barwaye mu bitaro, hakubiyemo 17 bari barwaye izindi ndwara, hamwe n'abaganga cyangwa abaforomo 40.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni iby'ingenzi ko twita ku bantu, cyane cyane abaganga, abashinzwe ubuzima, abagize umuryango, incuti ndetse n'abaturanyi bahuye n'abantu barwaye indwara zandura.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kwirinda indwara ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; gukoresha udupfukamunwa two mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa two mu bwoko bwa N95 (# 1860s) bifasha mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Umwenda w'ubuvuzi ufasha umuntu ufite uburwayi kwirinda ko amazi ava mu mubiri we ajya mu mwuka cyangwa mu bintu, aho ashobora gutangwa n'abandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa N95 gusa (umwimerere # 1860s) ni two dushobora kurinda virusi nibura kuva kuri 10 kugeza kuri 80 nm, kandi 5% gusa ya virusi ni yo ishobora kuyirinda burundu; SARS-CoV-2 ifite uburebure bungana n'ubwa SARS-CoV kandi byombi bifite hafi 85 nm.
Kubera ko ibice byayo bishobora kwinjira mu gihe habonetse udupfukamunwa dutanu tw'abaganga, abaganga bazajya bahura n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa N95 (# 1860s) aho kwambara udupfukamunwa twa muganga.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abaganga bagomba no kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ibanze kugira ngo bakomeze kugabanya amahirwe yo kwandura virusi.
Nanone kandi, virusi ishobora kwandurira mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga w'inzobere mu buvuzi yabonye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; birashoboka ko virusi yamwinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye yababaraga.
Ni yo mpamvu abaganga bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa indorerwamo mu gihe bavura abarwayi.
Ku bantu bose bari mu duce dufite cyangwa dushobora kuba dufite virusi, ni ngombwa ko bose bakaraba intoki kenshi cyane bakoresheje isabune, kuguma mu rugo, kwicungira ukwabo no kwirinda guhura n'abantu bashobora kuba barwaye.
Metero ebyiri ni intera yemewe abantu bagomba kugumana n'umurwayi.
Ibi ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye nk'indwara nshya mu bantu, isa cyane na SARS-CoV nk'uko byavuzwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, yagombye kuba yarabaye imbogamizi mu Bushinwa kubera ko abantu benshi bazi neza uko SARS yavutse mu 2003.
Ariko kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara cya Wuhan yahumurije abaturage avuga ko iyi virusi nshya idashobora gukwirakwira mu bantu, ko idashobora gukwirakwira mu bantu kandi ko bigoye kuyirinda no kuyirinda.
Iyo nkuru yatumye abantu batita ku byo bari biteze, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari cyitegura kwizihiza umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi, bituma igihe cy'ingenzi cyo gukumira icyorezo cya Wuhan kirangira.
Ikigo cyo mu Bushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya indwara gishobora kuvana isomo kuri ibyo bintu bibi, maze kigakora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo kizakemure icyo kibazo.
Urugero, ibigo by'ubuvuzi bigomba (1) kuba byitonda mu gihe bitanga ibiganiro ku mugaragaro kubera ko abaturage babyizera kandi bikaba bishobora guhindura imyifatire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) kwita ku byo abaganga batanga aho gutegereza raporo z'abaganga cyangwa abayobozi; (3) gufata ingamba zikomeye zo kurwanya icyorezo mu gihe kigitangira aho gushishikariza abantu kucyemera; no (4) gushyiraho uburyo bukwiriye kandi bw'ingirakamaro bwo gufasha abaturage kurushaho kumenya iby'indwara z'ibyorezo no kuzipima no kugira icyo bakora mu gihe habaye ibyago.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi, mu gihe twandikaga iyi nkuru.
Kubera ko virusi ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV, kandi ibimenyetso byayo bikaba bisa n'ibya COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye SARS isubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Ariko kandi, hari itandukaniro rinini hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na ryo ryangombwa mu gukumira iyi ndwara no gukiza abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko n'abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi ni yo yibasira cyane kandi ihitana abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko.
SARS izaba ari yo izaba yishe abantu benshi kurusha COVID-19 (10,91% kuri 1,44%).
Abantu banduye COVID-19 bakwirakwiza virusi nubwo baba badafite ibimenyetso, ariko abantu banduye SARS bakwirakwiza virusi mu gihe gusa barwaye cyane, bityo bigatuma COVID-19 idashobora gukwirakwira cyane kurusha SARS.
Ibi byasobanuraga impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwira cyane kandi mu bice byinshi kurusha SARS-CoV.
Iyo SARS-CoV-2 isuzumwe mu buryo busanzwe bwa RNA, birashoboka ko nta muntu uzongera kwandura COVID-19.
Icyakora, abantu barokotse bashobora kongera kwandura.
Ibyo byose byatumaga virusi ikwirakwira mu bihugu byinshi.
Kugira ngo ubushakashatsi kuri COVID-19 bugende neza, hari ibintu byinshi by'ingenzi bigomba gukosorwa, urugero:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo hasuzumwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ihuriye ku kigero cya 96% na SARS CoVs ebyiri zaturutse ku mbogo, ntabwo twakwemeza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse ku mbogo.
