Muri iyi nyandiko, twashubije ku gitekerezo cyatanzwe n'abagize komite y'igihugu ishinzwe ubuzima muri Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa, maze dutanga ibipimo by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze by'uko umuntu yakwifata n'uko yakwemera gukira nyuma y'ibyavuzwe mu gitabo cya nyuma cy'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 (verisiyo ya karindwi).
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cyiswe icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (COVID-19) cyiswe SARS-CoV-2.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyizeho icyiciro cya COVID-19 nk'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2, umuryango wacu washinze inama yo kwihutisha ibiza, nk'uko byatangajwe ku rubuga rwa interineti n'ibiro by'ubuvuzi bya gisirikare ku itariki ya 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka, yagiye isomwa cyane.
Ariko kandi, mu gihe COVID-19 ari icyorezo, ubumenyi n'ubushishozi dufite ku birebana n'iyo ndwara buzazamuka buhoro buhoro dukurikije ibyagezweho n'ibyagiye bikoreshwa mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ubu buryo bwo gupima indwara n'imiti bizakoreshwa buzahora buhuje n'igihe.
