Hariho uburyo bwo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina gusa n'umuntu mubana mu nzu, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso.
Gushyingirwa mu ngo ni ngombwa ku bantu bafite COVID-19 ndetse n'abakekwaho kuyirwara.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze inama ku bijyanye no gushyira abantu mu kato. Leta nyinshi zashyizeho amategeko cyangwa zasaba ko abantu bose bajya mu kato mu duce dufite ubwandu.
Amategeko yo gushyira abantu mu kato akomeye cyane agenga abantu bashobora kwandura.
Ababa baragiranye umubano wa bugufi n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 n'ababa bavuye mu turere cyangwa uturere dufite ubwandu bukabije bagomba kuguma mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, kugabanya cyangwa kugabanya cyangwa kucyandura.
Gufata ingamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu rwego rwo gukurikirana abantu no gushyira mu kato abanduye no gukora ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu no gukingira abantu kugira ngo bakure indwara mu baturage.
Mu gihe bigoye guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, intego ni ukugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu idini.
Umurimo wo kurangiza no kugabanya umusaruro ushobora gukorwa mu buryo bumwe.
Kugabanya ubwandu bisaba ko hakorwa byinshi mu guhindura Panama ku buryo umuntu umwe ashobora kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo 1.
Ibi byagabanyije ibyago byo kuba ibitaro by'abaganga byuzuyemo abantu benshi, kandi bituma haboneka igihe cyo gukora urukingo n'umuti.
Ibikorwa bitari iby'ubuvuzi bishobora gufasha mu gukwirakwiza indwara zandura harimo gukaraba intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa, kwigunga; amategeko y'amadini agenga gutandukanya abantu n'abandi, gufunga amashuri no kubuza abantu benshi kwifatanya; imyizerere y'amadini mu bikorwa nk'ibyo; no kwirinda ibikorwa by'isuku mu mujyi. Andi mategeko akomeye yafashwe mu Bushinwa igihe ikibazo cy'uburwayi cyari cyikomeye, gushyira umujyi wose mu kato no gufunga imihanda.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byashyizeho amategeko yo kurwanya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangiye gukora ibizamini by'ibanze, ishyiraho gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi ikumira ingendo z'abantu.
Singapuru yatanze amafaranga ku bantu bari bariyemeje kwiyicarira bonyine, kandi ishyiraho ibihano ku bantu batayishyize mu bikorwa.
Taiwan yazamutse mu gukora udupfukamunwa no kurwanya ababikora cyane. Ibyabaye mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika bigaragaza ko (guhagarika icyorezo ariko bigatuma kitongera gukwirakwira) ari uguhagarika (guhagarika icyorezo) bikomeye cyane.
Amategeko agenga imikorere y'ibitaro ashobora gufasha abakozi b'ibitaro kugabanya umubare w'abari mu bitaro ku bice bibiri bya gatatu, kandi agabanya kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa n'abababara.
Gukumira bishobora kuba byiza ariko bigomba gukomeza gusa mu gihe virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa ku munsi urukingo ruzaba rwarageze), kuko gukwirakwira byongera igihe abantu batakomeje gukingira.
Gushyiraho amategeko y'igihe kirekire yo guhagarika icyorezo bizagira ingaruka ku bukungu n'idini.
Nta muti wa COVID-19 uhari, ariko hari uburyo bwo kuwukoresha, ndetse no kugerageza imiti ikoreshwa.
Kunywa umuti ukomoka ku buvuzi, kunywa amazi, no gusinzira bihagije bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Iyo bikomeye cyane, umuti wa oxygène, guterwa ibintu mu muhogo, n'imashini zo guhumeka bishobora gufasha.
Kuvurwa hakoreshejwe imiti ya siporo bishobora gutuma umuntu asobanukirwa ibintu mu buryo butari bwo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemewe kuvurwa n'inkingo, ariko hari izindi virusi zikiri mu bushakashatsi ku bijyanye no kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko imiti yo mu rugo n'iyo mu baturage ishobora gufasha mu guhangana n'ibi bimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19.
