Aba barwayi bari mu muhanda wo mu isoko rya Huanan, aho bagurishaga amatungo, kandi hari abavuga ko virusi yaturutse mu nyamaswa, abandi bakavuga ko yaturutse mu nyamaswa cyangwa se ko ari zoonotic.
