Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, abantu 9.336 bo mu itorero rya Gikristo, 1.261 cyangwa 13% bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo ni yo yari ifite umubare munini w'abanduye ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
