Nyuma y'ibyo, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangiye gukora ibizamini nyuma, bituma icyorezo cy'icyorezo gitangira gukomera muri iki gihe.
Ibikoresho byo gupima byatangijwe na leta muri Gashyantare, nta byemezo bya leta by'ibikoresho by'ipimisho by'ibanze (mu mashuri, mu bigo cyangwa mu bitaro) byemejwe kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, kandi hari inama nyinshi ku bantu bashobora kwipimisha guhera mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (gusaba impapuro z'umwanzuro).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru Washington Post cyatangaje mu magambo make ibipimo 4000 byakozwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru cyitwa Atlantic cyatangaje ko hakozwe ibizamini 14.000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko: Abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'ibyangombwa by'ubuvuzi bategereje amasaha menshi cyangwa iminsi myinshi kugira ngo basuzumwe. Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Amerika rwamenyekanye i Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yavuze ko ari icyorezo cyugarije ubuzima bw'umugi, nyuma y'aho igihugu cyose cyakurikiyeho.
Amashuri muri Seattle yafunzwe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, nyuma y'uko mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose afungurwa. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yatangarijwe uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyagaragaye mu ishuri rya Imperial College mu Bwongereza.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku masezerano y'akazi yo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus, agera kuri miliyari $8.3 z'amadolari y'Amerika, agamije gufasha inzego z'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu mu kurwanya icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubucuruzi yahagaritse imirimo yo gukora mu muhanda, ahagarika amateraniro, kandi ategeka abantu gukorera mu ngo zabo.
Imikino na yo yahagaritswe. Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko gahunda yo gufunga inzira yari igenewe ibihugu byose by'u Burayi, ariko atari Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yashyize ahagaragara ayo mategeko kugira ngo ajye ahagaragara mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yavuze ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu cyateye imbere, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga y'igihugu yo kurwanya icyorezo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyiriza amasaha yo gukora muri Amerika mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari kimaze kugaragara mu mijyi 50 na Columbia, ku ya 23 Werurwe, New York yari ifite abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, umubare munini kurusha Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku itariki ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bifasha, kuko umubare w'abarwayi ku munsi wariyongereye uva kuri 2.0 ugera kuri 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, i New York hari abantu 32.308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ni zo zari zifite umubare munini w'abanduye coronavirus ku isi, nyuma y'Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari abantu 400,335 banduye, naho 12.841 barapfuye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, leta zunze ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko Perezida Trump azashyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda abantu ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda 1.000, bwageze i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hapfuye abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri New York, abanduye barenze 100,000 ku itariki ya 3 Mata. Abantu banenze White House kubera ko batishimiye cyane ibyo bavugaga ku bijyanye n'imikorere y'abanyeshuri n'abahanga mu bya siyansi mu bijyanye no gutunganya igihugu ndetse n'ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo byanditswe na Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Hari abantu bamwe na bamwe batemera ko Trump ari we ugenzura icyo kibazo.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo bishimira ko Amerika yishingikirije cyane ku by'ubucuruzi bw'ibanze bw'u Bushinwa.
Inyigo yo gukora inzira yo gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya virusi yasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Health Roadmap mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Ishyirahamwe ry'indege ryavuze ko mu mwaka wa 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari byo bihugu bya mbere byagize abagenzi benshi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byari ibibuga by'indege byahuriragamo abantu benshi baturutse i Wuhan.
Bali ni cyo gihugu cya mbere mu bihugu 20 bya mbere byafashwe nk'ibanze mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, mu gihe ibihugu byo muri Ositaraliya byatangaje ko byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo. Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Ositaraliya yashyize ahagaragara gahunda y'ibikorwa byo guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bigomba kumenyekana ku bijyanye na COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira mu bikorwa amategeko agenga umuhanda n'ibyavuzwe ku cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangiye ikibazo cy'umutekano.
Mu gihe imodoka za bisi zari zifunze i Wuhan na Hubei, abaturage benshi bari bateganyijwe kwimura abanyapolitiki babo muri utwo duce, mbere y'indege z'igihugu, ku bw'amabwiriza yatanzwe n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, u Buyapani, u Buhindi, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, u Bufaransa, u Budage, Arjantine na Tayilande, ni byo bihugu bya mbere byatanze abantu.
Pakisitani yavuze ko izakura umwe mu bayobozi bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 cyangwa ababyeyi babo, ifashijwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abapolonye, Abashinwa n'Abahindi bari baragiye muri Polonye, Ababiligi na bo baramanutse bajya muri Brezili.
Aba Brezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu gace kari hafi y'akarere k'abimukira muri Brezili.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 bo muri Kanada (176 bari mu ndege, 39 bari mu ndege ya leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajya mu kato mu kigo cya CFB Trenton mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 bari bavuye i Wuhan, yageze ku cyambu cya CB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi bo muri ako karere bafashe toni 277 z'ibinyabuzima byabo babishyira mu kigo cyo ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyari cyateganyijwe ko abantu bahatirwa kuguma mu ngo zabo, bakamarayo iminsi 14.
Indege yo gukuraho abantu muri Nouvelle-Zélande yagezeyo ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, kandi abari bayirimo (bamwe muri bo bakaba bari baturutse muri Ositaraliya no muri Pasifika) bagiye kwihisha mu mujyi wa Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zizakuraho Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Pricess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 129 bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton ho muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yatangiye guhungisha abantu muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya leta ya Sud Afrika yafashe abantu 112 ba Sud Afrika.
Ibizamini byakozwe, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus bagumye mu gihugu kugira ngo barinde abandi.
Abantu bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bonyine basuzumwe basanga nta ndwara bafite.
Ibizamini byafashije abantu bo muri Sid Afrika ndetse n'abari mu ndege, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi, abashinzwe umutekano, bose bagumye mu kigo cya Ranch Resort mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gukura abasirikare mu gihugu cya Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (Delarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri, Irani n'ibindi) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri Kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gutanga imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byazahajwe na virusi, ndetse n'itsinda ryo muri Chicago ryohereje udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo muri Hubei ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahaye OMS miliyoni 100 z'amadolari yo gukora ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no gufasha no kurinda abaturage bafite ibyago muri Afurika no mu Majyepfo ya Aziya.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa 3.16million i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango wa Croix Rouge wo muri Singapuru watangaje ko wari wateguye inkunga y'amadolari y'amanyamerika miriyoni 2,26 yo gufasha u Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe i Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwatanze toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Maleziya yavuze ko izatanga toni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi Amerika yavuze ko miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ari mu nzira yo gukoreshwa mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abarwayi ba Wuhan barangiye, igihugu cyakomeje kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abaganga kugira ngo bafashe Abataliyani kurwanya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi witwa Jack MA yohereje ibikoresho byagenewe gupima indwara bigera kuri miriyoni 1, imirasire ya maso miriyoni 6 n'imyambaro yo kwirinda indwara ibihumbi 60 i Addis Abeba muri Etiyopiya, kugira ngo bihabwe Umuryango w'Afurika yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje i Panama ibikoresho 5.000 byo gupima indwara, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka.
Bwana Ma yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Kanada. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bitewe impungenge n'udupfukamunwa n'ibikoresho byo gupima indwara by'Abashinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yanze ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus by'Abashinwa byerekanaga 30% gusa by'ibisubizo by'ukuri, hanyuma Ubuholandi busubiza udupfukamunwa 600.000 tw'Abashinwa kubera ko twari twononekaye.
U Bubiligi bwashubije mu gihugu cyabwo udupfukamunwa 100.000, bwari butekereje ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Icyakora, hari ibihugu byo muri Amerika y'Epfo n'ibyo muri Afurika byitabiriye neza inkunga y'u Bushinwa.
OMS yashimye cyane abayobozi b'u Bushinwa kubera imihati bashyizeho mu kugenzura no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yashyize itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye hagati ya 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ko batigeze bagaragaza neza uko bakemuye iki cyorezo, n'icyorezo gisanzwe, aho abayobozi bazajya batanga amakuru mashya buri gihe kugira ngo birinde gutera ubwoba abaturage mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, nyuma y'icyemezo cy'ubutegetsi cyo guhagarika ingendo zose muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo nta nama yatanzwe na OMS, ari ikintu cyiza cyerekana ko ibikorwa by'ubutabazi byihutirwa nubwo ari ahantu hamwe, avuga ko ari ikintu kitari cyigeze kibaho mu rwego rw'ubuzima. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kumenya ko hari umuntu wanduye hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi ko umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu wiyongereye, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga (USPPI), cya gatandatu kuva PHEIC yafata ingamba zo guhagarika icyorezo cy'ibicurane cya 2009 .
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ishobora gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere bidakoresha ibitaro byiza.
Nyuma yo gushyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi hagati y'ibihugu kandi ko OMS itazemera ko abantu bahagarika ubucuruzi cyangwa ngo bemererwe gukora ingendo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye ibihugu gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, ivuga ko ubufasha ari ingenzi mu bihugu bitarabona uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, ndetse n'iyo yaba ari yo.
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "kugabanya ubukana ari kimwe no koroshya uburyo bwo kuvura" asaba ibihugu "gukora ubu cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari izina ry'icyorezo.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, António Guterres, yemeye "guha imbaraga Umuryango w'Abibumbye wose kugira ngo urwanye".
Itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ibihe bidasanzwe ryatangiye gukora, rituma umuryango w'abibumbye wose wifatanya muri iyo ntambara, OMS ivuga ko izatuma "ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuzima buhinduka mu gihe izindi nzego zizaba zigiye kugenzura imibereho y'abaturage, ubukungu n'iterambere ry'abaturage".
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya OMS mu Bushinwa ryatangiye gukorana mu rwego rwo gufasha abaganga mpuzamahanga na OMS gufasha Ubushinwa kurwanya iki cyorezo no kureba uko ubukana bw'iki cyorezo n'uburyo cyandurira abantu binyuze mu mahugurwa n'inama mu nzego z'ibanze z'ibihugu no gukora ingendo zo kureba ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kurwanya iki cyorezo mu karere no mu gihugu, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu. Ku itariki ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko nubwo tutashobora kwita iki cyorezo icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuba byiteguye.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abantu muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo rigenzure icyo kibazo. Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi ari "cyinshi" ariko ko kigomba kuba "cyinshi cyane", ari na cyo kigero cyo kugenzura cyane kandi giteye ubwoba.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe ibibazo by'ubuzima by'ihungabana muri OMS, yaburiye itangazamakuru ko Iki ari ikintu cy'ingenzi isi yose igomba kwitaho: Nimukanguke.
Yavuze ko hari igihe virusi ishobora kuza kandi igomba gutegurwa, avuga ko hakwiye gushyirwaho ingamba zifatika zigamije gukumira ko ibintu byongera kuba bibi ku isi.
Ryan yongeyeho ko amakuru ariho ubu adashobora guha abayobozi b'ubuzima ubushobozi bwo kuvuga ko ari ubwandu, avuga ko kuvuga gutyo bisobanura ko tudafite icyizere cy'uko abantu bose ku isi bazaterwa n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS ifite impungenge z'uburyo ikwirakwira cyane kandi ifite imbaraga, ndetse n'ukuntu nta cyo twakoze. Abantu benshi banenga OMS kubera ko babona ko idashobora gukurikirana neza ibi bibazo, nko kuvuga ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi bw'ubuzima kandi ko iyi virusi ari icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 6 Mata, abantu 733.000 bashyize umukono ku ibaruwa isaba ko umuyobozi mukuru wa OM, Tedros Adhanom, yegura.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri Loni zemeje ko hakwiye kubahirizwa uburenganzira bwa muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'abahanga ryemeje ko abantu bose bagomba gukizwa, kandi ko ubutegetsi ari bwo bufite inshingano yo kubikora.
Abo bantu bavuze ko kuba nta mafaranga afite cyangwa ngo agire ubwisungane mu kwivuza ari byo bituma habaho ibikorwa by'urugomo.
Impuguke zavuze ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, hakubiyemo abamugaye, abantu bo mu moko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi, abatagira aho baba, abakene, imfungwa, impunzi ndetse n'abantu bo mu bwoko butandukanye, bagombye kwitabwaho na leta.
Leta z'ibihugu zagiye zifata ingamba zo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Bwikorezi n'Iterambere (OECD) ryashyizeho gahunda yo gushyiraho uburyo bushya bwo kurwanya iki cyorezo, harimo n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu by'ubuzima ku isi, gifasha mu kubaka ubuzima bw'abantu n'ubukungu bw'isi mu kurwanya ingaruka z'ingendo z'abantu n'ingendo, gifite ikoranabuhanga mu bya politiki, kandi gifasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi bihugu no guhangana n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zashinje leta y'Ubushinwa, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, na Edouardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili Jair Bolsonaro, uburyo bakemura iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'Abashinwa (CCP) birukanywe mu kazi kubera ko bari kugenzura ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko abaturage batishimiye uburyo abayobozi bakorera muri utwo turere.
Hari abanyamakuru bemeza ko impamvu y'iki cyemezo ari ukugira ngo umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa Xi Jinping arinde abantu guhura n'iki cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ko coronavirus yatangiriye i Wuhan, ndetse banatekereza ku birego by'Amerika n'Ubutaliyani by'uko COVID-19 ari yo yatumye ibaho.
Guverinoma ya Amerika iyobowe na Donald Trump yavuze ko coronavirus ari virusi y'Ubushinwa cyangwa virusi ya Wuhan, avuga ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwabaye ibanga ry'icyorezo cyugarije isi, bamwe bavuga ko ayo magambo ari urwikekwe rushingiye ku moko, ndetse ko ari n'ikimenyetso cy'uko ubutegetsi bwe budafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Daily Beast yabonye telegarama ya leta ya Amerika yerekanaga ibiganiro by'inama y'umutekano w'igihugu, ariko bavuga ko byose byerekezaga ku Bushinwa gusa.
Bazatubwira ko tugomba kugerageza guhagarika amakuru yose, haba mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ndetse no kuri televiziyo. Politico, ubushakashatsi ku by'ububanyi n'amahanga, na Bloomberg bavuga ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bigize gahunda yo kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi ushinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko "hariho gushaka ubutegetsi binyuze mu bumenyi bw'ibinyoma no mu buryo bwo gutanga".
Borell yavuze kandi ko Ubushinwa buzatuma habaho amagambo y'uko, mu buryo butandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ari cyo gihugu cya mbere cyabaye incuti nziza kandi yiringirwa.
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Siriya, Venezuela na Irani, kandi buvuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Amasikini 100.000 Jack Ma yohereje muri Cuba yafashwe ku itariki ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Nanone kandi, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zarashinjwe ko zari gufatira imfashanyo zari zarahaye ibihugu by'amahanga.
Kandi hari ibindi bihugu bishobora kuba byaravuganye ku bihereranye n'ibitambaro byo kwipfuka, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya n'u Busuwisi; Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Nanone kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho byo guhumeka umwuka byari bigomba kujya muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utishyize hamwe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwagize icyo bukora ku nyungu z'ibihugu byombi.
Birumvikana ko atari ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubumwe bw'u Burayi.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cyo kuri telefoni yagiranye na Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya, Vladimir Putin yohereje mu Butaliyani abasirikare b'Abarusiya bafite abaganga, imodoka z'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyavuze ko "umutegetsi ukomeye" wanze kuvuga izina rye, yavuze ko 80 ku ijana by'inkunga Rissue yatanze "ari nta cyo byari bimaze cyangwa nta cyo byari bimaze ku Butaliyani".
