Ibizamini bya coronavirus y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na SARS-CoV-2 bifitanye isano na virusi, birimo uburyo bwo kumenya virusi n'uburyo bwo kumenya udukoko tw'umubiri twubaka ubwirinzi.
Kuba hari virusi mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, ikora ubushakashatsi ku virusi ya corona RNA.
Iki cyuma cy'ubushakashatsi gifite intego yo kumenya RNA ya SARS-COV-2.
Izo nsoro zikoreshwa mu kuvumbura indwara nshya cyangwa indwara z'inzobere.
Gushakisha udukoko tw'umubiri (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima no kugenzura abantu.
Iperereza ry'umubiri w'umuntu rigaragaza umubare w'abantu barwaye, ndetse n'abafite ibimenyetso bike cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara n'ubw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bishobora kumenyekana hakurikijwe ibipimo by'iyi miti.
Kubera ko ibipimo by'ubwandu bidashobora kuboneka, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe agaragaza uko virusi ishobora gukwirakwira mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze gikora ibizamini ku baturage 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu buryo ibihugu bitandukanye byakoze ibizamini.
Nanone kandi, iryo tandukaniro rishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku gipimo cy'abapfa, gishobora kuba gito cyane mu bihugu byinshi.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gusuzuma imiterere y'ibinyabuzima hakoreshejwe polymerases (rRT-PCR) bishobora gukorwa hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'imyuka bivanze n'uburyo butandukanye, harimo no gufata ibice by'ibinyabuzima mu mazuru cyangwa mu cyondo.
Ubusanzwe, ibipimo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa se mu minsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR ryakorewe ku mukondo w'umuntu ushonje ritanga ibisubizo byiza gusa mu gihe indwara yaba imaze icyumweru.
