Hari n'ibindi bihe gukaraba intoki neza biba ari umuco wo kwirinda indwara, urugero nko gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere; nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora, gukorora; nyuma yo gukora ku byondo by'amatungo cyangwa ku byondo by'amatungo; na nyuma yo gukora ku byondo.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu bake ni bo bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki bwakorewe mu bihugu 54 mu mwaka wa 2015, bwagaragaje ko imiryango 38,7% ikoresha isabune. Mu mwaka wa 2014 ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite 97% by'abanduye, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zikaba zari hafi kuri 77%; Ubushinwa bukaba bwari bufite 23% by'abanduye. Imirimo myinshi irimo guhindurwa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga mu gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'amasaha y'ikiruhuko. Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'amasomo ni uburyo bwo kwigisha abana mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Icyiciro cy'ingenzi cy'ubuzima bw'abana cyatangijwe na Minisiteri y'Uburezi ya Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo guteza imbere ubuzima bw'abana no kubatoza kwiga.
Gukura amenyo n'ibishyimbo kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi n'umuti wo gukaraba amenyo, ni bimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi bigize gahunda y'igihugu.
Abagore bo muri Indoneziya bakoresheje ubwo buryo, maze bagira umusaruro mwiza cyane.
Kugira ngo umubiri ukomeze gukira, wongeraho isabune cyangwa umuti wica udukoko.
Inshingano ikomeye y'isabune n'imiti yo gukiza indwara ni ukugabanya ubukana bw'ubuvuzi, no kongera imbaraga zabwo.
Amazi ni yo yonyine ashobora gutuma uruhu rugira isuku, kubera ko amavuta na poroteyine byo mu butaka bitanyurwa n'amazi.
Icyakora, iyo amazi ahagije ari yo atuma isuku irushaho kuba nziza.
Kubera ko isabune ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora kuba irimo mikorobe y'abantu bayikoresheje mbere.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku birebana n'uko isabune ikwirakwiza mikorobe, bwagaragaje ko idashobora kwanduza abantu, kubera ko ikoreshwa mu gusukura.
Ariko kandi, CDC ivuga ko amazi arimo isabune ari yo afite akamaro cyane mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Abenshi bavuga ko ari byiza ko abantu bita ku buzima bwabo bakoresha amasabune afite umuti wica mikorobe.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bihamya ko abantu bashishikarizwa gukoresha imiti yica udukoko twanduza ibimera cyangwa imiti yica udukoko twanduza ibimera.
Ariko kandi, isabune akenshi iba irimo umuti urwanya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, irimo mikorobe nyinshi zandura ku isi.
Ku bw'ibyo, nubwo imiti yica udukoko itarimo isabune, hari igihe iba idafite imbaraga nk'iz'iyo bakoresheje.
Uretse ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwo hejuru kandi by'ibanze birinda uruhu, imiti isanzwe ishobora kuba irimo aside (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lastic acid) nk'ibishobora gutuma uruhu rugira pH, aside benzoic yica mikorobe, n'ibindi bintu byangiza uruhu (aloe vera, vitamini, menthol, ibikomoka ku bimera). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon mu by'ubuzima rusange bwagaragaje ko isabune yo mu mubiri wacu igira akamaro cyane kuko isabune irimo umuti wa antibiotique irimo triclosan mu kurwanya indwara no gukuraho mikorobe mu biganza.
Amazi yo gukaraba intoki adafite umuriro nta mikorobe yica.
Iyo umubiri ushyushye cyane, indwara ziterwa n'agakoko gatera indwara zigenda zikura vuba.
Ariko kandi, amazi y'amazi afutse, arimo isabune, arusha amazi akonje gukoreshwa mu gukuraho amavuta, imyanda n'udukoko.
Ariko kandi, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babitekereza, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi y'abantu bidakoresha intoki.
Umushongi wo gusukura intoki cyangwa umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ni umuti wo gusukura intoki udakoresha amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gukaraba intoki itarimo amazi (nanone yitwa imiti yo gukaraba intoki, imiti yo gukaraba intoki cyangwa imiti yo gukaraba intoki) yatangiye gukoreshwa cyane.
Byinshi bikoreshwa mu gukoreshwa kwa isopropylique cyangwa ethanol hamwe n'ikintu nka Carbomer (polymer ya acrylic acid) hamwe na gel, cyangwa humectant nka glycerine hamwe n'amazi, cyangwa umukungugu kugirango ukore neza kandi ugabanye imbaraga zo gukama za alkali.
Kongera umwuka wa idorojeni-peroxide mu mazi bituma umuti wica mikorobe ugira imbaraga nyinshi.
Imiti yica mikorobe, mikorobe zidakira umuti w'imbuto (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, na za virusi (harimo SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, inkingo, ibicurane n'indwara y'umwijima) hamwe n'imitobe.
Imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga 70% yica 99,97% (igabanya log na 3,5, ikongera decibel na 35) ya mikorobe mu biganza nyuma y'amasegonda 30 imaze gukoreshwa na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (igabanya log na 4 kugeza kuri 5) ya mikorobe mu biganza nyuma y'iminota 1 imaze gukoreshwa. Imiti yo gukaraba intoki ifite ubushobozi bwo kwica mikorobe ariko ntiyica izindi virusi.
Imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga ntiyihanganira virusi yitwa norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), ikunda gukwirakwiza virusi mu byondo. Birakenewe ko hakoreshwa imiti yo gukaraba intoki cyangwa inzoga nyinshi cyane ku buryo iminwe yose iba yumye cyangwa yanduye.
Mbere na nyuma y'amaboko yombi no hagati y'amaboko kandi ukarabe intoki mu masegonda 30 kugeza amazi, ifu cyangwa gel yumutse.
Ibi bisaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki, akazikoraho intoki zombi. Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara kivuga ko ari byiza gukaraba intoki aho gukoresha umuti wo gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye cyane.
Imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa cyane kubera ko yoroshye gukoresha kandi ikora vuba, ariko ntiyasimbura isuku y'intoki, ahubwo ikoreshwa gusa iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari.
Gukoresha imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga kenshi bishobora gutuma uruhu rwumera nk'urwumye, keretse iyo wongeyemo imiti yo gukaraba intoki.
Gushyiraho glycerine n'ibindi bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma inzoga zidakora neza cyangwa zikabura imbaraga.
Mu igerageza ry'urukingo ku bantu, imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga irimo ibintu bigabanya ubukana bw'intoki, ikora ku ruhu gake kandi idakomora intoki cyane kurusha amasabune cyangwa imiti yica udukoko.
Incuro nyinshi, uruhu rwabo ntirwakoraga ku buryo ruhinduka ibara, ntirwakoraga ku buryo ruvamo imbuto, kandi ntirwakira imiti irimo inzoga cyangwa ibindi biyobyabwenge.
Abantu batangiye gukundwa cyane no gukoresha imiti ituma uruhu rutera ibara ry'umutuku, aho gukoresha isabune n'amazi yo gukaraba intoki.
Nubwo amazi yo gusukura intoki ari meza, nta cyo atwara intoki, ahubwo azisukura.
Ni yo mpamvu umuti wo gusukura intoki ukoreshwa mu kwirinda indwara nyinshi, ugereranyije n'isabune n'amazi, kuko utuma habaho indwara zikomeza kwiyongera.
Ingaruka z'ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki bitagira inzoga zigenda zishingira ku byo biyongeraho n'uburyo bikoreshwa, kandi biragaragara ko ari byo bifite inzoga nke cyane kurusha izirimo inzoga nyinshi.
Mu myaka ya vuba aha, imiti irimo chlorure ya benzalkonium yari ifite ubushobozi bwo kwica mikorobe, mu gihe inzoga zo zari zifite ubushobozi bwo kuzimya indwara, wenda bitewe n'uko ziterwa n'uko umuntu yaba afite ibisebe byinshi mu ruhu.
Mu bihugu bikennye, abantu bashobora kugura isabune bakayisimbuza umukungugu cyangwa ibumba.
Umukungugu cyangwa ibumba bishobora kuba bikomeye kurusha amazi, ariko ntibigira imbaraga nk'iz'isabune.
Ikintu kiduhangayikishije ni uko ubutaka cyangwa umukungugu birimo mikorobe bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira aho kuzirinda.
Nanone kandi, umukungugu w'isabune uratunganya, kuko iyo uvanze n'amazi uba urimo umuti wa alkaline.
OMS ivuga ko mu gihe nta sabuni ihari, ukwiriye gukoresha ivumbi cyangwa umusenyi.
Amategeko yo gukaraba intoki akoreshwa n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, agamije gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara, ni aya akurikira:
Gukaraba intoki n'amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Bavuze ko gukoresha amazi ari yo y'ingenzi cyane kubera ko abakinnyi bicaye hamwe bashobora kuba bafite mikorobe, kandi ko ubushyuhe bw'amazi nta cyo buvuze.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, harimo no ku mugongo w'intoki, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'iminwa.
Isabuni yica mikorobe, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki neza kandi mu gihe kirekire iyo bakoresheje isabune, aho gukoresha amazi ubwayo.
Jya ushyiraho n'isabune nibura amasegonda 20.
Iyo mibare ifasha mu gukuraho udukoko twanduye, kandi iyo umuntu amaze igihe kirekire atwika, bica udukoko twanduye.
Jya ukaraba intoki neza mu mazi atemba.
Gukoresha isuku bishobora gutuma intoki zongera kwandura.
Gukomesha mu mwenda cyangwa mu cyuma.
Ibiganza byumutse bishobora kwandura. Ahantu henshi usanga abantu badakoresha neza isuku ni ku rutoki, ku nkokora, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'intoki.
Amasahani n'ibisate by'iminwa bishobora kuba birimo mikorobe.
Akenshi, abantu batanga inama yo gukoresha amavuta yo gusiga intoki kugira ngo umuntu atazagira intoki zumye, kuko intoki zumye zishobora kwangiza uruhu kandi bigatuma umuntu arwara indwara zidakira.
Amavuta menshi yoroheje ashobora gukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki aho amazi n'isabune bitagaragara, urugero nko gusuka amazi mu gikoresho cyangwa igikombe gifite imyobo n'imyanda, cyangwa se gukoresha umukungugu mu gihe bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Iyo amazi ari make (urugero, mu mashuri yo mu byaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), nta buryo bwo kubungabunga amazi bukoreshwa, urugero nko gukoresha utuzi tw'amazi n'ubundi buryo buhendutse.
Tippy-tap ni uburyo bworoshye bwo gukoresha imifuka y'amazi ishyirwa hejuru kandi ifungwa n'umugozi, kandi ifashwe n'umugozi kugira ngo isuke amazi ku biganza no ku kintu cyo gukaraba.
Kumesa intoki neza ni ingenzi ku buzima, ariko hari impaka nyinshi ku buryo bwo kumesa intoki neza mu mibereho ya benshi.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe bugaragaza ko umwenda wo gukaraba intoki ari wo utanga umusaruro mwiza kurusha imashini ikora imyenda yo gukaraba intoki.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi buciriritse bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster mu mujyi wa Londres, bufashwa n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyitwa European Tissue Symposium, cyakoze ibikoresho byo kumesa intoki, kugira ngo basobanukirwe itandukaniro riri hagati y'ibikoresho byo kumesa intoki, imashini yo kumesa intoki n'imashini nshya yo kumesa intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki mu bikoresho bikaraba intoki, umubare w'abantu banduye mu ntoki wazamutseho 194% n'uw'abantu banduye mu ntoki wazamutseho 254%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki mu bikoresho bikaraba intoki, umubare w'ubwandu mu ntoki wazamutseho 42% n'uw'intoki wazamutseho 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki mu kintu gikomesha intoki, umubare w'ubwandu bwa virusi wagabanutse ku kigero cya 76% ku ntoki no ku ntoki ku kigero cya 77%.
Imashini yo gukaraba intoki, ikora umwuka ku muvuduko wa metero 180 ku isegonda (650 km/h; 400 mph), ishobora kohereza mikorobe nto mu ntoki mu bice by'ubwonko no mu bandi bantu mu butinyanka ku metero 2.
Gukoresha imashini yo kumesa intoki byangiza mikorobe iri ku metero 0.25 uvuye ku gikoresho.
Imyenda yo gukaraba intoki yagaragaje ko nibura hari uturemangingo duto duto twanduye. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, bwakurikiranye uburyo bwinshi bwo gukaraba intoki.
Dore uko imibare y'abantu banduye nyuma yo gukaraba intoki itandukaniye:
Hari ibigo byinshi by'inganda bikora imashini zimesa intoki, kandi hari itandukaniro hagati y'imashini zimesa intoki n'imyenda imesa intoki.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umwambaro wo gukaraba intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'urugendo, mu gihe nta sabuni n'amazi bihari.
Imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga igomba kuba irimo inzoga zigera kuri 60%.
Nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuhanga mu bya fiziki wo muri Hongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko umuti wo gukaraba intoki ushobora gutuma indwara zidakwirakwira mu bitaro, ni bwo abantu benshi batangiye kuwukoresha.
Hari ibikoresho byinshi bifasha abarwayi kwibuka ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha imiti nk'iyo byagabanyije ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki ni byiza cyane, bigomba kumara amasegonda 15, ukoresheje amazi n'isabune nyinshi cyangwa amavuta ku ntoki zose.
Bagomba gukubita ibiganza hamwe mu gihe bafatanya.
Niba hari umwanda uri ku ntoki, ushobora kuwukuraho ukoresheje ikintu runaka.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora gusigara mu mazi y'intoki, ni iby'ingenzi ko twirinda ayo mazi kandi tukayapfuka n'igitambaro gitanduye.
Nyuma yo kumesa, ugomba gukoresha umwenda wo kumesa kugira ngo ufashe amazi (kandi ukingure urugi iyo ari ho hose).
Ibyo bituma intoki zitandura.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku ni ukuvanaho umwanda (bakteri) no kuwubuza gukwirakwiza ku bandi.
Ikinyamakuru cyitwa New England Journal of Medicine cyavuze ko mu bitaro, umubare w'abantu batigeze bakaraba intoki, kandi ko abaganga n'abaforomo benshi bakunze kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakabatera mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza no gukoresha uburyo bworoheje bishobora kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara z'amaraso ku kigero cya 66%.
Dushobora kubona inama za mbere z'ishyirahamwe ryo gukaraba intoki kandi zishobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwayo kugira ngo abantu bose bashobore kuzisuzuma.
Whitby na bagenzi be bakoze ubushakashatsi bw'ingirakamaro.
Imashini zigurishwa zishobora gupima no kuvuga niba intoki ari nziza, niba uburyo bwo gukora isuku bwasabwe buhagije.
