mbere yo gukora uyu murimo wo gukaraba intoki,
Nyuma yo kuvura umurwayi. Gukoresha umuti urinda indwara mu gusukura intoki (amasabuni  afite umuti cyangwa amasabune  yica mikorobe) bifasha umuti wo gukaraba intoki kugabanya indwara.
Gucukura intoki mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa ahantu hashobora kuba hari mikorobe nyinshi ni ngombwa. Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi, niba ari ngombwa, hakoreshejwe pompe ishobora gufungura cyangwa gufunga amazi, umuti wa chlorhexidine cyangwa wa iode, igitambaro kitagira mikorobe cyo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kuzirinda, n'isupu itagira mikorobe yo gukaraba imyanda n'ikintu kitagira mikorobe cyo gukaraba imyanda mu ntoki.
Inzahabu zose zigomba kuvanwaho.
Iyi nkingo igomba gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki no mu ntoki kugeza hagati y'intoki, cyane cyane mu minota 2-6.
Nta mpamvu yo gutinda guteka (iminota 10).
Mu gihe usukura, ugomba gufunga inzira kugira ngo amazi ari imbere y'amaboko yawe atajya inyuma y'amaboko yawe.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, ugomba gukaraba intoki ukoresheje igitambaro kitagira mikorobe kandi ukambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutangire gukwirakwira, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa se ukoresha umuti wo kuvura imyanda mbere na nyuma yo kuvura umurwayi.
Mu bipimo by'ibitaro by'indwara ya staphylococcus, byaragaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zabayeho nyuma yo gukaraba intoki mu kigero cya 20% cya mbere, naho inyungu nkeya zabayeho nyuma yo gukaraba intoki ku kigero cya 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabune byongera inshuro eshatu ubukana bw'imiti ikwirakwiza mikorobe ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabune irimo umuti wa antibiotique. Mu buryo butandukanye no gukaraba intoki n'umuti wa antibiotique urimo inzoga, gukaraba intoki n'isabune irimo umuti wa antibiotique mu masegonda 30 bigabanya ubukana bw'imiti ikwirakwiza mikorobe ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije n'isabune irimo umuti wa antibiotique.
Ariko isabune n'amazi birusha imbaraga imiti irimo inzoga mu kwanduza virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane A na Clostridium difficile spores mu ntoki. Imihati yo guteza imbere isuku y'amaboko mu bitaro ishobora kuba irimo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, gutuma abaturage babona imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga nyinshi, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kwivuza bufite akamaro mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, biragaragara ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ibintu bihenze, ko ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu agire ubuzima bwiza, ndetse ko ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu abone ibyokurya byiza.
Ariko kandi, kubura amazi meza, isabune n'aho gukaraba intoki mu ngo, ku mashuri no ku kazi, bituma abantu bose badashobora kugira akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki.
Urugero, mu bihugu byinshi bya Afurika, ahantu ho gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa rusange cyangwa bwa rusange ntihariho, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, kuba abantu bataraba bakaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kuba ari ibintu bisanzwe, ariko si ukubera ko nta mazi n'isabune bihari.
Gushyigikira no gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora gutuma habaho amategeko, bigatuma abantu bakoresha amagambo akomeye yo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bagira ihinduka rikomeye mu mibereho yabo.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikorwe neza, ni ngombwa ko hagira umuntu usuzuma ibyo akora kandi akabigenzura.
Gusuzuma ubushakashatsi 70 byerekanye ko gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki mu byaro ari ingenzi mu bihugu bikennye, ariko kurwanya gukaraba intoki ni ibintu by'ingenzi. Urugero rumwe rwo gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Amategeko Atatu" ya UNICEF, ashishikariza amashuri gukora ibintu byoroheje kandi bihendutse, bigatuma abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki n'isabune, mu bindi bikorwa by'isuku.
Amashuri amaze kwigisha amahame y'ingenzi, ashobora kongera kubigisha amahame y'ingenzi.
Gushyiraho ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa by'iterambere mu gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bw'uko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kugabanya uburwayi n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'uko ubutumwa bufasha abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF irashishikariza abantu gushyiraho emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bundi buvuga ku mubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, buvuga ku mubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki mu gihe cy'ibyigisho bya DALY.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaza intoki n'isabune ari byo bihenze cyane kurusha ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba intoki, urugero nk'amazi n'ubundi buryo bwo kwiyeza.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi, urugero nk'ababyeyi bavuka cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse bari mu bitaro  katangirijwe mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abantu babiri batangije gahunda yo gukaraba intoki: Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhongiriya wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, umwongereza  washinze ubuforomo".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bemeraga ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi, zitwaga miasmus.
Mu myaka ya za 80, indwara ziterwa n'ibyokurya hamwe n'izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubuvuzi, byatumye Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda, gitera inkunga cyane isuku y'amaboko, kivuga ko ari ingenzi mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2020, byatumye ibihugu byinshi byita ku isuku y'amaboko hakoreshejwe isabune mu kwirinda icyorezo nk'iki.
Urugero, mu Budage, ibyapa byanditseho ngo "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki" byashyizwe hafi y'aho abantu bakaraba intoki, ku biro no ku bibuga by'indege.
Imvugo ngo "kwitandukanya n'ikintu" isobanura ko umuntu atemera inshingano cyangwa ngo yivange mu kintu runaka.
Byatangiriye mu gice cya Bibiliya cya Matayo kivuga ko Ponsiyo Pilato yogeje intoki igihe yafataga umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko byaje kuba amagambo akoreshwa cyane mu bihugu bivuga Icyongereza.
Mu nkuru ya Shakespeare yitwa Macbeth, Mama Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki kugira ngo ahumanure umwanda wari mu bwenge bwe, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko yari azi neza ko yari yarakoze ibyaha bikomeye kandi ko yari yarashishikarije umugabo we kubikora.
Abantu bagaragaye ko iyo bibukijwe ibintu bibi cyangwa bakabyibuka, bakaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi ko bishimira cyane ibikoresho bifasha abantu gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kwibuka ibyo, akenshi ntibakora ibikorwa by'isuku by'ingutu, urugero nko gukora umurimo w'ubwitange.
Mu madini, gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo ni ikintu cy'ingenzi cyane. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi aho gukoreshwa isabune mu gukaraba intoki, ni imigenzo y'amadini menshi, urugero nk'Ababahayi, Abahindu, Abazubahwa n'Abaterabutatu mu idini rya Kiyahudi, Aba-Lawa mu idini rya Gikristo na Aba-Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Nanone kandi, Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasiki, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu, basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kurya.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda COVID-19 ku kazi
Ingamba zo kwirinda COVID-19 mu kazi zikoreshwa mu rwego rw'umutekano n'ubuzima mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda ku kazi bushingiye ku hantu hakorerwa akazi n'uburyo bukoreshwa, ku ngaruka zo gukora ibintu bishobora guteza impanuka, ku buryo indwara zandura mu karere, no ku ngaruka abakozi bashobora kugira ku cyorezo cya COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Urwego rw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye rwita ku Buzima n'Umutekano (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike ni akazi gasaba ko abantu bakorana n'abandi bakorana bakagira aho bahurira, gakenera ko hakorwa ingamba z'ubwirinzi, urugero nko gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, indwara z'ubuhumekero, no kugira isuku no gukora isuku mu kazi.
Akazi k'akaga gaciriritse ni akazi gasaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa hafi y'abantu azi cyangwa bashobora kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba barwaye bitewe no guhura n'abantu benshi cyangwa gukora ingendo mu bihugu byinshi.
Ibyo ni na ko bimeze ku bakozi bakorana n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'abo mu mashuri, ku kazi n'ahandi hantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Kwirinda ibyago muri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba rusange zo kwirinda, bisaba gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero bifite imyuka ihumeka cyane, kwirinda mbere yo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina, no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA igenzura abaganga n'abakozi bo mu nzu y'ubuvuzi ku bantu bazwi ko bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi, kandi igenzura abantu bakora imirimo yo gutunganya cyangwa gukora ku bipimo bya aerosol, cyangwa abafata ibipimo by'abantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bashobora kuba bayifite.
Kugira umutekano usesuye ku bantu bakora imirimo ishobora kuba ari ukujya kwihisha mu mazu afite umwuka mubi, no kwambara imyambaro yo kurinda abantu.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora guteza akaga gakomeye ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba barirengagiza akazi kubera ko barwaye, kubera ko baba bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa kubera ko batinya ko bashobora guhura n'umuntu urwaye.
Uburyo bwo gukora ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka, bitewe n'uko abantu baba bashaka kugura cyangwa se uburyo bwo kugura (urugero, kugura mu gihe cy'ibirori cyangwa kugurisha ibintu ku nzu n'inzu).
Icya nyuma, bashobora guhagarika ingendo zo gutwara ibintu mu turere dufite ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Imyiteguro igaragaza ibyago byo mu kazi no mu kazi, hakubiyemo abantu uzajya uhura na bo, ibintu bishobora gutuma habaho impanuka mu ngo no mu bindi bice, n'akaga abakozi bashobora guhura na ko, urugero nk'abageze mu za bukuru cyangwa abarwayi badakira.
Nanone kandi, ivuga uko umuntu yakwitegura kugira ngo yirinde ibyo byago, kandi ikagaragaza uko umuntu yakwitegura kugira ngo yirinde ingaruka ziterwa n'iyo ndwara.
Gutegura icyorezo no kucyirinda bizakorwa hakurikijwe amategeko y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo ni ukugabanya ubukana bwacyo mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura indwara z'uburwayi, gukomeza gukora, no kwirinda ko ibyo byangiza ibikorwa by'abandi bakorana.
Ibyo ukora bizaterwa n'uko uburwayi bwagufashe.
Gushyiraho ingamba z'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe ni uburyo bwemewe bwo kurinda ubuzima bw'abakozi n'ubw'abaturage mu buryo bushoboka.
Mu bihugu bidashobora gukuraho COVID-19, uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana na yo ni ukwitegereza ibyuma, nyuma yo gusuzumwa n'inzego z'ibanze, hanyuma amaherezo umuntu wese ahabwa ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Gukoresha imashini mu gihe cy'akazi bisobanura kwirinda akaga mu kazi, ariko ntibitume umuntu atakaza umuco mwiza wo gukora, kandi bishobora kuba ari uburyo bwiza bwo gukora ibintu.
Gusuzuma abayobozi ni uguhindura uburyo bwo gukora akazi, bigasaba ko umukoresha cyangwa umukozi ahindura uburyo akora.
Ibikoresho byo kwirinda (PPE) ntibigira imbaraga nyinshi ugereranyije n'ibikoresho bya mashini cyangwa iby'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda impanuka zimwe na zimwe.
Uburyo bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa ukurikije ibyago byugarije umukozi, niba ari ngombwa (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka), kwambara neza kandi buri gihe, kubungabunga, no gushyiramo bundi bushya, niba ari ngombwa, no kubukura neza, kubogeza, gutunganya cyangwa kujugunya kugira ngo bidashobora kwanduza.
Dukurikije uko Urwego Rushinzwe Umutekano n'Ubuzima (OSHA) rubivuga, impanuka z'akazi z'inshuro nke ni izirebana n'abantu bake cyane n'abo bakorana.
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda gukwirakwiza indwara mu kazi buzwi ni ugukaraba intoki kenshi, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, mu gihe bafite indwara z'ubuhumekero, gupfuka umunwa cyangwa amazuru mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa bakorora, kugira imyenda yo gukaraba n'aho kuyishyira, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo gutumanaho cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'ubutabazi mu gihe ari ngombwa, no gukomeza imyitwarire myiza yo gusukura no gusukura aho bakorera.
Kumenya hakiri kare abantu bashobora kuba barwaye no kubashyira mu kato ni uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu ku kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara n'Ubuvuzi (CDC) cyasabye abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ifata imyakura (asthma) kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe umuriro, umuriro n'ibindi bimenyetso bizashira mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nta miti yo kugabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti yo kuvura ibindi bimenyetso, kandi hashyirwaho amategeko agenga ikiruhuko gikwiriye, kwemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi abakozi bagomba kumenya ayo mategeko.
Dukurikije OSHA, ibyago byo mu kazi byo mu rwego rwo hagati bifitanye isano n'abantu bahura cyane cyangwa bari hafi ya metero 1.8 z'umuntu ufite COVID-19 cyangwa ukekwaho kuyandura, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko iyi ndwara yandurira mu gace utuyemo cyangwa mu kazi, cyangwa bitewe n'abantu baherutse gukora ingendo mu bihugu birimo ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ibi bireba abakozi bahura n'abantu batandukanye nko mu mashuri, aho bakorera, n'ahandi hantu hakorerwa ibikorwa by'abantu benshi. Kubungabunga ibikoresho by'abantu nk'aba bisaba gushyiraho ibirahuri by'umwuka bikomeye, gukora neza imashini z'ubwonko, kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ubwonko nk'ibikoresho bitwara umwuka, no gushyiraho udusasu tw'amadirishya ku bakiriya. Abashinzwe umutekano mu bihe by'akaga benshi bazasaba abakozi bakomeje kuba mu ngo, bagire inama kuri interineti aho kuba mu bwiherero, gushyiraho amategeko yo kwirinda ingendo zitari ngombwa mu bice by'abandura COVID, gukora ibiganiro n'ibiganiro bishingiye ku bibazo by'akazi, gutanga amahugurwa mashya ku bijyanye na COVID-19 no kwirinda indwara, nko mu gihe cy'akazi, gutanga amabwiriza ku bakiriya, kubasaba kwambara imyenda yo kwirinda cyangwa gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwonko, kubwira abantu ko bagomba kwirinda gukoresha imyenda yo mu buryo bw'ibanga, guhagarika imirimo, no gutanga amabwiriza ku bakiriya babo, kubabwira ko bagomba gukoresha imyenda yo mu ntoki n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwoko bwose, ndetse no kubamenyesha abakozi ko bagomba gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwonko mu gihe cy'akazi.
Abakozi bo muri urwo rwego ntibakenera cyane gukoresha ibikoresho bifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi ni ukumutandukanya n'abandi bantu mu ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umukozi w'abagenzi kugira ngo amwiteho, no kumuha agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko yambara igitambaro mu kanwa no mu mazuru igihe arimo akorora cyangwa asonza.
Abakozi bo mu cyumba cy'indege bagomba kwambara imyenda y'ubuvuzi mu gihe bita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa iyo bakorana n'umunyururu cyangwa ikindi kintu gishobora kumutera indwara, kandi bakagira amakenga mu gihe umurwayi afite umuriro, ubwonko budahita cyangwa se arwaye umwuka.
Imikandara n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa nyuma yo gukoresha bigomba kujugunywa ahantu hakwiriye, kandi ahantu hose hashobora kuba hari ubwandu hagomba gusukurwa no gukorerwa isuku. Ku bwato bw'abacuruzi, hakubiyemo n'abagenzi n'abandi bantu bari mu bwato, kwirinda bisobanura kwirinda gukora ingendo mu gihe urwaye, no kwihutira kujya kwa muganga mu gihe umuntu uri mu bwato afite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by'uburwayi.
Ni byiza kugenzura ubuzima bw'umurwayi aho ari. Ku mashuri cyangwa ku bigo byita ku bana, CDC izasaba ko aho ari hagumaho igihe gito kugira ngo hasukurwe cyangwa se hasukurwe indwara iyo ari yo yose yaba yaragaragaye ku ishuri, yaba ari indwara yogeye cyangwa itariho.
Mu gihe uburwayi butakwirakwira cyane, ushobora gukoresha uburyo bwo kugabanya abantu guhura, urugero nko guhagarika ingendo, amakoraniro, n'ibindi bikorwa by'ingenzi, urugero nko gukora imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa kuririmba mu mashuri cyangwa gusangira muri resitora, ndetse no gushyira intera hagati y'ibiro, gutegereza igihe cyo kuza cyangwa kuva, kwirinda kujya gusura abantu bitari ngombwa, no gukoresha ibiro by'abaganga bitandukanye ku bana bafite ibimenyetso by'ibicurane.
Iyo ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara bugwiriye cyane mu karere utuyemo, uretse uburyo bwo kwirinda, ushobora gufunga amashuri mu gihe kirekire. Ku bapolisi bakora akazi kabo ka buri munsi, CDC ivuga ko ibyago byabo ari bike.
Abapolisi bagomba guhura n'abantu bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19 bagomba gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga, harimo no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Iyo umuntu afashwe, aba bantu bagomba gusukura no gukaraba ibikoresho byabo mbere yo kubikoresha, bakabikora bakoresheje ibikoresho by'isuku, kandi bakagendera ku mabwiriza yo kwirinda no kujugunya ibikoresho bya PPE, hamwe no kwirinda no gukaraba imyenda.
OSHA isuzuma ko bamwe mu bakora mu by'ubuvuzi n'abakora mu nzu y'ubuvuzi bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa se ko bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi.
Ibikorwa byugarije ubuzima harimo kubyara, kwita ku barwayi, gukora mu mavuriro, no gutwara abarwayi bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19.
Bajya mu kaga gakomeye cyane iyo bakoresheje aerosol, cyangwa bakagira ibipimo by'abantu banduye cyangwa bashobora kuba banduye COVID-19.
Imikorere ya aerosol ni imikorere nka intuba, kuvura ububabare, bronchoscopy, cyangwa imikorere cyangwa ibindi bizamini by'amenyo, cyangwa gutora imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ibyago bikomeye byugarije abakozi bo mu nzu y'ubuvuzi bw'abapfuye ni abafasha mu gutunganya imibiri y'abantu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 cyangwa abantu bakekwaho kuba barwaye; bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi kurushaho iyo bamaze gukora ibizamini by'indwara ya COVID-19 nyuma yo gupfa. Ikindi kintu gishobora kubateza ni ugukorera mu byumba by'abantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa abantu bakekwaho kuba barwaye, ndetse no gukora imirimo yo gutunganya za aerosol.
Mu bitaro bimwe na bimwe no mu bigo byita ku bapfuye, gukoresha umwuka uhumeka bishobora kuba ingirakamaro.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe urwego rwa 3 rw'ubuziranenge.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatanze inama y'uko abantu bagomba kujya mu byumba by'abategereje bitewe n'uko bareba niba bashobora kwandura COVID-19. Uretse kuba hari uburyo bwo gukora ibikoresho byo guhumeka bikoreshwa na PPE, OSHA yavuze ko abantu bagomba gukora ahantu hatandukanye n'abantu bafite SARS-CoV-2 bamenyekanye ko bayirwaye, cyangwa se bayirwaye, ndetse no gukora ibikorwa by'ubuhumekero.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka byemewe na NIOSH N95 cyangwa ibindi byiza kurushaho bigomba gukoreshwa cyane mu rwego rwo kwirinda indwara z'ubuhumekero nko gupima imikorere, guhugura no gusuzuma kwa muganga.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bufasha abantu kurinda no gukora neza. OMS ntiyemera ko abantu bahumeka mu maso hose, kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo guhumeka kandi idashobora gukwirakwira mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS izasaba gusa ko abantu bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bakora ibizamini.
Ku bantu bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, kubitaho, cyangwa gutwara abantu barwaye COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo gukoresha aerosole, OMS yemeza gukoresha udupfukamunwa, udushumi tw'ubwirinzi, cyangwa ibikoresho byo kurinda mu maso, ibirahuri, n'ibikoresho byo mu mutwe.
Mu gihe ukoresha aerosol, ujye ukoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka bya N95 cyangwa FFP2 aho gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Kubera ko ibikoresho bya PPE bitagera ku bantu bose, OMS yashyizeho amabwiriza yo kugabanya gukoresha cyane ibikoresho bya PPE mu buvuzi bwo mu rwego rwa terefone, kugabanya abantu batashobora guhura n'abandi, nko gufungura amadirishya, kureka abaganga bakinjira mu cyumba cy'umurwayi wa COVID-19, gukoresha ibikoresho bya PPE by'ibanze gusa, gukomeza gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero by'ubwoko bumwe mu gihe bivura abarwayi benshi, kurinda no gukoresha neza ibikoresho bya PPE, no kudashishikariza abantu gukoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe badafite ibimenyetso.
