Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za terefone zigamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba barwaye icyorezo cya 2019-20 cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Hari abantu benshi basabye ubufasha, kandi hari n'ahandi leta yafashe ingamba zo kubushyigikira.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kugenzura abantu bwakoreshwaga mu gukoresha telefoni.
Abantu ntibakunze kuvuga ko ikora ubushakashatsi ku bwihisho bw'abantu, urugero nk'uburyo bwo kugenzura aho abantu bari.
Mu bintu by'ibanga by'ibanze, harimo ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth bifasha umuntu kumenya niba hari telefoni z'abantu zikiri hafi.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bigiye gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukoresha Bluetooth muri Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu ifasha abaturage kumenya niba bari hafi y'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
Ibi bikorwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa, muri Singapuru, hakorwa porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ikoranabuhanga cya Macédoine cyashyizeho iyi porogaramu, igamije gufasha abantu bose, ndetse ikazahabwa leta. Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yashyizeho porogaramu ya StopKorona!, ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth rizajya rigena niba umuntu yanduye ku giti cye, kandi rigashyigikira intambara ya leta yo kurwanya indwara.
Iyi porogaramu yateguwe n'Urwego rw'Ububanyi n'Amahanga rushinzwe Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga mu rwego rw'Ubuzima.
Ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyo porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play na Apple App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo kugenzura abantu imaze kugera kure, kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'iyi irimo gukorwa muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle Zélande bifuza gukoresha porogaramu ya Singapore TraceTogether na BlueTrace. Uburusiya burimo gukora porogaramu izagenzura abantu bafite COVID-19 batuye i Moscou, igamije kubakurikirana kugira ngo batagira aho bava.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge ushinzwe umutekano, yavuze ko hari byinshi bishobora gukorwa kuri iyi porogaramu, urugero nko kugenzura ibyiza by'urubuga, ndetse no kugabanya ubushobozi bwo gukora neza kubera ko porogaramu ishobora gufasha abantu benshi.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ikoranabuhanga ryanduye coronavirus, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku miryango ishobora gushyira porogaramu kuri App Store, igashyiraho abakozi ba leta cyangwa abandi bantu bazwi.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ayo mategeko.
Abantu benshi baharanira uburenganzira bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite bw'abantu mu rwego rwo kugenzura, bibaza niba hari ahantu hakwiriye ho kubungabunga ubuzima bw'abantu cyangwa niba hazakurwaho nyuma ya coronavirus
Amesty International n'izindi nzego zigera ku 100 zashishikarije abantu gushyiraho amategeko agenga ibikorwa byo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amahame arindwi leta ishobora gukurikiza:
Gukurikirana ko ibyo bikorwa bikorwa mu buryo buhuje n'amategeko kandi mu buryo bukwiriye.
Igihe cyo guceceka kigomba kuba kiri hano;
Imibare izakorwa gusa kubera COVID-19;
Bagomba kugenzura amakuru y'abantu n'amazina yabo kandi ntibagomba kubigisha ibyo bakora;
Gukoresha orudinateri mu gihe umuntu atangiye kwanga abandi;
Gutanga imibare y'abantu batari mu mirimo igomba gukorwa hakurikijwe amategeko yanditse;
Hakwiye kubaho uburyo bwo kurinda abaturage no kubafasha mu gihe hari umuntu wahuye n'ibibazo bitewe n'uyu mukozi;
Kugira uruhare mu bikorwa by'abaturage bose, harimo n'abashinzwe ubuzima n'abadafite ababarinda. German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) na bo banditse inama zabo.
Google na Apple biteganya ko bazakuraho ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura iyo gahunda mu gihe nta mpamvu ikiriho.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byatanze uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu kuri interineti aho gukoresha porogaramu, bityo abantu ntibagomba kuba bafite porogaramu kandi bashobora kwirinda ko abantu bakurikira.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikirana umuntu hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kumurebesha amaso byemewe.
Nanone kandi, kureba kuri orudinateri bigira ingaruka ku bintu bitari ngombwa.
Icyakora, si ko buri sisitemu yose igomba kumenya aho umuntu ari; hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kugenzura abantu bufite aho buhuriye n'ubuhinga bwo gutumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hagiye hatangira gushyirwaho porogaramu z'ubucuruzi zisaba ko umuntu atishyurira kuri interineti.
Muri iyi porogaramu, abantu bakoresha amakuru aturuka ahantu hatandukanye, urugero nko kuri telefoni, ku ikarita ya banki, bakayakoresha mu kubwira abantu ubutumwa bugufi bw'ubwandu.
Kandi babimenyesheje abagiye muri iyo nzira, na leta yatumye abantu bose bamenya aho hantu, ibyo bikaba ari byiza mu mategeko kubera ko byakozwe mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya MERS cyabaye mu gihugu.
Amakuru ashobora kuboneka ku buntu kuri porogaramu nyinshi na interineti. Ibihugu nka Ubudage byashakaga gukoresha uburyo bwo gucunga umutekano w'abaturage.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, nta nyandiko yari yarasohotse.
Gukurikirana amakuru biramenyekana cyane, mu bushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe kuva mu mwaka wa 2013. Ku itariki ya 7 Mata 2020, abanyeshuri barenga 12 bari barimo gukora uburyo bwo kugenzura amakuru, urugero nka Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) igaragaza telefoni iri hafi.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni uburyo bwo gukora mu buryo bwo hanze, kandi nta mabwiriza yo kuyikoresha aboneka. Porotokaramu zo hanze zirimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact (TCN. fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN) Privacy Sensible Protocols na Mechanisms for Telephone Tracking.
Muri ubwo buryo, nta makuru y'ibanga azigera aboneka, kandi buri kintu cyose kizakorwa hakoreshejwe telefoni.
Itsinda ry'abikorera hamwe na MIT Media Lab barimo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rwo gukwirakwiza amakuru y'abantu ku giti cyabo, hamwe no kugenzura aho abantu bahurira cyangwa aho bahurira kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Byaturutse ku gitabo cy'umwimerere Apps Gone Rogue: Gucunga amakuru yawe bwite mu gihe cy'icyorezo  cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020.
SafeTrade ifasha ikoranabuhanga ryo kubika amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye kugira ngo abantu bashobore guhitamo niba bashaka gutanga amakuru y'aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima bwabo ku bandi bantu no ku nzego za leta, ariko ntibahindure amategeko agenga kubika amakuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga TCN ryatangijwe n'itsinda ry'abantu b'abanyamuryango b'ibihugu byombi, ryemeje uburyo bwo kugabanya ibyago by'abantu, no gufasha kuzana interporability y'isi binyuze mu gukurikirana no gukangurira abantu gukoresha porogaramu, byari ngombwa kugira ngo isi yose itangire kuyikoresha.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, leta ya Singapore yatangaje ko ifite uburyo bwo gukoresha BlueTrace ikoreshwa n'abakozi bayo.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga bya Android na iOS byatangaje ko hatangiye umushinga wo gufasha abantu gukurikirana amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cyabo, ariko kandi ugamije kurinda ubuzima bwite bw'umuntu, ukoresheje ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy na Cryptography.
Nanone kandi, hasohotse inyandiko igaragaza uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga.
