Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'icyubahiro ry'iki cyorezo ari "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yasobanuye ko CO ari corona, VI ari virusi, D ari indwara, na 19 ari icyorezo cyamenyekanye bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Aho kugira ngo abantu bahitemo kwirinda kwereka umuntu ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'intoki mu karere runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko runaka bw'indwara cyangwa umuryango runaka w'abantu, urutonde rw'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso by'amazina byatanzwe mu bihugu byose by'isi byatangiye gukoreshwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa SARS-CoV-2 (Sindrome ya Coronavirus yo mu Kirere).
OMS ikomeza ivuga ko ikoresha "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu gutanga amakuru.
Iyo virusi n'iyi ndwara byombi byitwa gusa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'icyorezo byombi byitwaga "coronavirus" na "Wuhan coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yashyizeho 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV mu byiciro by'indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibimenyetso by'indwara n'indwara zikurikiraho mu mwaka wa 2015 aho yashyizeho izina ry'indwara n'indwara.
