Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibihugu byinshi ku nkingo na dosiye za COVID-19 bwatangiye gukorwa n'inzego za leta, inzego z'ubushakashatsi n'iz'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije icyitwa "Igerageza ryo Gushyigikira" kugira ngo ryigenzure rigamije kumenya ingaruka z'iyi miti ya virusi itera SIDA, igaragaza ko hari icyizere cy'uko izagufasha.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwakozwe, ariko inzego nyinshi zirimo gukora cyane kugira ngo zikore inkingo zifite ubushobozi bwo gukira.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku bwoko bwa SARS-CoV bwagaragaje ko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira abantu bugomba gushakishwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi batangiye gutekereza ku buryo bakoresha bakubaka urukingo rwa virusi yose.
Gukoresha virusi, yaba iyicisha cyangwa iyicisha, bigamije kwihutisha igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umuntu ku cyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, urukingo rw'urwego ruto, bugamije gukora urukingo ruzatuma abadepite b'umubiri bagira ubushake bwo kurwanya virusi.
Ku kibazo cya SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko poroteyine ya spicule-S ari yo ituma virusi ikora ikorana na ACE2 receptor.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rw'umushongi wa ADN (DNA cyangwa RNA, ni ikoranabuhanga rishya mu kuvura indwara).
Inkingo zigeragezwa zikoresheje ubwo buryo zigomba kuba ari ibipimo by'umutekano n'ubuziranenge. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, inkingo za mbere zo mu bitaro zatangijwe n'abantu bane b'abakorerabushake i Seattle.
Urukingo rugizwe n'imiterere y'imiterere y'umubiri w'umuntu utari wandukuwe kuri virusi ituma umuntu arwara. Ingaruka z'ubwiyongere bw'imiterere y'umubiri w'umuntu zituma umuntu arwara indwara zigeze zitekerezwa ko zishobora kuba mu cyiciro cy'intambara mu gihe cy'iterambere ry'urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko ibyo biracyari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga birimo gukorwa birenga 300 muri Mata 2020.
Hari ibizamini birindwi by'ubuvuzi by'indwara ya malariya byemewe, naho bine by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze byitwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga ni yo yateye imbere cyane mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa, aho ibipimo icyenda bya III bya remdesivir biri gukorwa mu bihugu byinshi bizatanga raporo mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Mata.
Igenzura ry'imiterere y'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi bw'urukingo rwa COVID-19 mu buryo bwemewe n'abaganga rigiye kuba muri Mata 2020.Ibipimo byinshi bya antiviral byateguwe birimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifitanye isano na interferon beta.
Ibimenyetso by'ibyiza bya remdesivir byatangiye kugaragara muri Werurwe 2020.
Ibyiza byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byagaragariye mu barwayi bahabwa imiti ya remdesivir.
Ibizamini by'ibanze bya Phase III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yakoreshejwe mbere mu kuvura malaria, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, mu byiciro bya mbere.
Ariko kandi, hari icyizere cy'uko intiti zizafata umwanzuro ku birebana n'ibyavumbuwe.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanze amabwiriza yo gukoresha chlorine.
Ikigo cya Wuhan Institute of Virology kivuga ko iyo umuntu ahawe dose imwe ya gamma buri munsi, inshuro ebyiri z'iyo dose ziba ari mbi cyane ndetse zishobora no kumuhitana.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rw'ibanze rwo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu ibanga mu buvuzi bw'abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze byerekana ko ingano yo hejuru ya ribavirin ari ingenzi mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide yashyizwe mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi bwa in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gukumira. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gutangiza poroteyine ya mbere ikoreshwa na poroteyine ya transmembrane serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi cyane mu kwinjiza SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhangana na ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine irimo cyangwa idafite azithromycin bufite imipaka ikomeye cyane ituma ishyirahamwe ry'abahanga mu by'imiti ryiyemeza kutabemerera imiti itarimo ubushakashatsi bwimbitse. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihangana na SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta n'akamaro ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igitutu cy'imiti gishobora kuba ari cyo cyorezo cya nyuma cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kuba ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa na cytokine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu cyiciro cy'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza ubushakashatsi buciriritse.
Ubu barimo gukora icyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ry'igihugu cyose mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza ku bantu bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Iyo mibare yafashwe ifatanyije n'ibipimo bya ferritin mu maraso, bigamije gukumira ubwiyongere, bikaba byitezwe ko ari byo bituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Interleukin-6 ikoreshwa mu buvuzi yemejwe na FDA mu cyiciro cy'ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje uburyo bwo kuvura indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo ya sitokine mu buryo butandukanye, mu cyiciro cy'imiti CAR T, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta kimenyetso cy'uko tocilizumab ari umuti w'ukuri wa CRS cyemezwa ku buryo bufatiweho cyangwa buteganyijwe.
Gutanga udukoko tw'umubiri twanduye n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umubiri by'abarokotse COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye, bizakurikizwa mu buryo bw'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo budafite urukingo n'uburyo bwo kuboneza urubyaro.
Hari abantu bagerageje gukoresha ubwo buryo ariko ntibyagira icyo bitanga.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwo kuvura antibodies zidakora cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu atagira ubwirinzi kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Hari ubundi buryo ariko, urugero nk'ubushishi bw'imiti n'imiti cyangwa se phagocytose y'ingirabuzimafatizo zishinzwe kurwanya indwara, bishobora kugira ingaruka.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe uduhimba tw'umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha uduhimba tw'umubiri tw'ubwoko bumwe twakozwe mu buryo bw'imashini, burimo burakorwa.
Umusaruro wa serum y'abarwayi bakize, uterwa na plasma y'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi ufite udukoko tw'umubiri tw'ubwoko bwihariye ku virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ishobore gukwirakwizwa vuba.
